Guéreins

Guéreins is a small French village in the Valley of the Saône river, 50 km North of Lyon. In the west stand the small mountains of the "Beaujolais" where the famous wine is produced. It is also the town where Stellarium was born :)

Author: Fabien Chéreau
Location: +46°6'31", +4°46'49.00", 83 m, Earth
